items.title: Who recently viewed a work item? by Matthew Manela is taking longer than expected to load.Learn More about this extension, including available support options.
items.body:
Hi,
Beginning of this week, the plug-in started to timeout when trying to load. Looking at the Debug Console, I can see that some errors are now being written:

```
TypeError: Cannot read property 'tagName' of undefined
    at RecentlyViewedList.n._getEnhancementOption (Controls.js:2)
    at RecentlyViewedList.t._createElement (Controls.js:2)
    at RecentlyViewedList.t._createIn (Controls.js:2)
    at RecentlyViewedList.t.createIn (Controls.js:2)
    at Function.t.createIn (Controls.js:2)
    at RecentlyViewedGroupView.initialize (RecentlyViewed.js:27)
    at recentlyViewedGroup.html:24
    at vss-bundle-ext-core-vLzRDA5ggzZEJHv-FnnlZ3C81KCQnL7UJ2rU5ikDvpj8=:305
    at Object.execCb (Content?bundle=vss-bundle-basejs-vSljho_k690hofnoiyEmz5e4nME3rw4wV1Y8HgrqvV9Q=:263)
    at pt.check (Content?bundle=vss-bundle-basejs-vSljho_k690hofnoiyEmz5e4nME3rw4wV1Y8HgrqvV9Q=:263)
```
Plug-in placeholder looks like this:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13141534/52067048-c173ac80-2547-11e9-94a3-1162d432ea0e.png)


Thanks for this great plug-in that we use daily! :)
Simon
